<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Indian Tourism</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
        }

        .cell {
            width: calc(33.33% - 20px);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            overflow: hidden; /* Added to hide overflow for hover effect */
            position: relative; /* Added for hover effect */
        }

        .cell:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px; /* Adjust the height as needed */
            object-fit: cover; /* Ensure the image covers the container */
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease; /* Added for hover effect */
        }

        .cell:hover .image {
            transform: scale(1.1); /* Added for hover effect */
        }

        .caption {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .description {
            margin: 10px;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #00695c;
        }

        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #f57c00;
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            .cell {
                width: calc(50% - 20px);
            }
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            .cell {
                width: calc(100% - 20px);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>Indian Tourism</h1>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="cell">
           <a href="/leh"> <img class="image" src="/bike.jpg " alt="Image 1"></a>
            <h2>Adventurous</h2>
            <div class="caption">Leh-Ladakh, Jammu and Kashmir</div>
            <p class="description">Embark on adrenaline-fueled adventures in Leh-Ladakh, Jammu and Kashmir, with thrilling activities like mountain biking and off-road jeep safaris amidst stunning Himalayan landscapes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cell">
            <img class="image" src="/boatraft.jpg" alt="Image 2">
            <h2>Adventurous</h2>
            <div class="caption">Rishikesh, Uttarakhand</div>
            <p class="description">"Thrill-seek in Rishikesh, Uttarakhand, India's adventure capital, with white-water rafting on the Ganges amidst Himalayan foothills, alongside bungee and cliff jumping."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cell">
            <img class="image" src="/thar.jpg" alt="Image 3">
            <h2>Adventurous</h2>
            <div class="caption">Jaisalmer, Rajasthan</div>
            <p class="description">Discover the golden allure of Jaisalmer, Rajasthan, with camel safaris and desert camping amidst ancient forts and palaces, offering a glimpse into the vibrant culture of Rajasthan.</p>
        </div>


        <div class="cell">
            <img class="image" src="/paraglide.jpg" alt="Image 4">
            <h2>Temples</h2>
            <div class="caption"> Bir Billing, Himachal Pradesh</div>
            <p class="description">Soar through the skies with paragliding in Bir Billing, Himachal Pradesh, India's paragliding hub, boasting stunning Himalayan vistas and a vibrant Tibetan culture.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cell">
            <img class="image" src="/boathouse.jpg" alt="Image 5">
            <h2>Temples</h2>
            <div class="caption">Kollam, Kerala </div>
            <p class="description">Explore the tranquil backwaters of Kollam, Kerala, aboard traditional houseboats, immersing in the serene beauty of lush landscapes and peaceful lakes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cell">
            <img class="image" src="/balloons.jpg" alt="Image 6">
            <h2>Temples</h2>
            <div class="caption">Pushkar, Rajasthan</div>
            <p class="description">Experience the vibrant charm of Pushkar, Rajasthan, with its iconic camel fair, ancient temples, and bustling bazaars, set against the backdrop of the Thar Desert.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- New Temples -->
        <div class="cell">
            <img class="image" src="/waterfall.jpg" alt="Image 7">
            <h2>Temples</h2>
            <div class="caption">Mawsynram, Meghalaya</div>
            <p class="description">Mawsynram, Meghalaya: World's wettest place, boasting lush landscapes, cascading waterfalls, and enchanting caves, offering a captivating natural experience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cell">
            <img class="image" src="/waterbike.jpg" alt="Image 8">
            <h2>Temples</h2>
            <div class="caption">Goa</div>
            <p class="description">Experience the vibrant beach vibes of Goa, with its golden sands, lively nightlife, and rich Portuguese heritage, making it India's coastal gem by the Arabian Sea.</p>
        </div>

       
    </div>
</body>

</html>
